Greetings folks!

To augment the bonding between students and the faculty of insti, Saathi
brings to you, F.I.E.S.T.A., an event first of its kind.

F.I.E.S.T.A is a minimela with fun activities and food stalls
E2B where students and faculty will come together to participate, eat
 and
have a funandfrolicfilled Saturday with games like
'Eating Competition' , 'Karaoke' , 'Do Not Laugh!'

